@page "/help"

<MudPaper Elevation="3" Class="p-4 help-container">
    <div class="help-header">
        <h1>Help & Support</h1>
        <p>Find answers, guidance, and support for using the Weather Forecast app.</p>
    </div>

    <MudDivider />

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section class="help-section">
        <h2 class="help-title">Overview</h2>
        <p>
            The Weather Forecast app provides users with up-to-date weather information, including temperature,
            conditions, and forecasts for their selected locations. You can save your favorite locations for quick
            access and track the weather easily.
        </p>
    </section>

    <MudDivider />

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="help-section">
        <h2 class="help-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <ul class="faq-list">
            <li>
                <strong>How do I search for weather in a location?</strong>
                <p>Use the search bar on the weather page to enter a city, then click the "Get Weather" button.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>How can I save a location as my favorite?</strong>
                <p>Once you view the weather for a location, you can save it by clicking the "Save as Favorite" button. Saved locations will appear on your favorites list for quick access.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Why am I not seeing updated weather information?</strong>
                <p>Ensure your internet connection is active. If the issue persists, try refreshing the page or clearing your browser cache.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <MudDivider />

    <!-- Troubleshooting Section -->
    <section class="help-section">
        <h2 class="help-title">Troubleshooting</h2>
        <p>If you're experiencing problems with the app, here are some steps to try:</p>
        <ol class="troubleshooting-list">
            <li>Refresh the page to ensure you're viewing the latest data.</li>
            <li>Clear your browser cache and cookies to fix any temporary issues.</li>
            <li>Ensure your browser is updated to the latest version.</li>
            <li>If you're using the mobile app, ensure it is updated to the latest version.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <MudDivider />

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="help-section">
        <h2 class="help-title">Contact Support</h2>
        <p>If you need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team:</p>
        <ul class="contact-info">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:kavin13102005@gmail.com">kavin13102005@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li>Phone: +91-7826022406</li>
            <li>Support Hours: Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM (EST)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can also visit our <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kavinrajsk?utm_source=share&utm_campaign=share_via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=android_app">creator page in LinkedIn</a> for more help.</p>
    </section>
